      "level": 1,
      "text": "Exterior Light Structure Description - Components"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Lighting Switch"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Lighting/turn signal switch signal is input to MICU."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "headlight"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Depending on the specifications, discharge lamps or halogen bulbs are used as the low-beam light source."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "taillight"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The tail light, brake light, rear turn signal light, and back light are all integrated."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "High mount stop lamp"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A high-mounted stop lamp is installed above the tailgate. LEDs are used as the light source."
    }
  ],
